h1. Welcome to _Rock Paper Scissors_

h2. Author
Andrea Caldera: andrea.caldera@gmail.com

h2. Build the application
{code}
cd $PROJECT_HOME
mvn clean install
{code}

h3. Run the application

h4. Interactive mode
Interactive mode offers you a basic UI for playing.

{code}
cd $PROJECT_HOME
java -cp target/rock-paper-scissors-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar org.andreacaldera.rockpaperscissors.App
{code}

h4. Demo mode

Demo mode showcases a game from two virtual players.

{code}
java -cp target/rock-paper-scissors-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar org.andreacaldera.rockpaperscissors.App -auto
{code}

h4. Advanced mode
Rock paper scissors lizard spock can be played by using the start-up option -mode=sheldon

{code}
java -cp target/rock-paper-scissors-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar org.andreacaldera.rockpaperscissors.App -mode=sheldon
{code}
or
{code}
java -cp target/rock-paper-scissors-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar org.andreacaldera.rockpaperscissors.App -auto -mode=sheldon
{code}

h4. Help
Help options available running

{code}
java -cp target/rock-paper-scissors-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar org.andreacaldera.rockpaperscissors.App -help
{code}
